@node "future" "   Future   "
                                  Future
                                  ------

    Who knows what the future may hold ?  The following features are ones 
    which I would like to implement:

    * MPEG Audio support (Dubious until I get an upgrade!) - This won't
      happen until the general Amiga user base upgrades!  Most people
      don't have the power to use to the max (including me!)

    * ListViews so that multiple files can be loaded.
 
    * Add more features, nicer gui, mui help bubbles, switch channels
      on and off, turn filter on or off, turn Name and type gadgets off,
      (Already done most of that!! :))

    * AREXX Port allowing other programs access to CoolMod. (DIFFICULT!!
      Help Wanted!!!)

    * Adding of more formats.  THX, Player 61 are possiblities :)
      I am finding integrating THX rather difficult!
@endnode

@node "Emailware" "   EMAILWARE   "
                                 Emailware
                                 ---------

    This means that if you use the program and like it you are to send me 
    an email or a letter that you use it. But this will change, those who
    have registered will not need to register again, but a change to full
    GIFTWARE or SHAREWARE may happen when it gets better.

    It should contain your snail mail address, your full name and what you
    like about it.  I WILL NOT give keyfiles to anyone who doesn't give me 
    their mail address.

    PLEASE DON'T MAKE ME ASK FOR IT IN THE EMAIL.  EVERY PERSON WHO HAS
    REGISTERED HAD TO BE ASKED!!!!  And make sure to put Coolmod in the
    subject line, or it may not be read at all.

    *** Scrap that, I am a student.  Totally skint.  I would appreciate 
    anything that you might want to send me.  But an email is the least.  
    Joe O'Conner has already stepped up and given me a couple of 16mb 
    SIMMS.  Nice!  Money, old Amiga games, old disks, old magazines,
    videos, tapes are all acceptable.  I like Oasis and the Verve!

    Or even send me something that you have written on the Amiga!!

    Most users that have registered have sent me nothing!!  I would
    appreciate something please!!!

    The most notable change about this will be that Coolmod will go full
    blown Shareware when I feel it is good enough, but those who register
    now get it free!!!

   @{b} BUT ABSOLUTELY NO DRUGS!@{ub}

    @{b}NO INTERNET CONNECTION ??@{ub}
    No problem, send me your details and an error free disk aswell as some
    money (or also a gift:)) for postage and I will send you a keyfile.

    My address:

