@node "usage" "Usage - I shouldn't have to do this!!   "
                                   Usage
                                   -----

    CoolMod is relatively easy to use.  But operation of it with the 
    different filetypes differs somewhat.

    When you are using sidtunes, the fastforward and rewind buttons 
    shuffle through the songs contained in it.  They don't fast forward 
    or rewind the individual songs.

    Also, due to the limitations of Play16, I am unable as yet to cause 
    Play16 to stop once it has been evoked.  I will rectify this later.
@endnode

@node "Installation" "   Installation   "
                               Installation
                               ------------

    * The CoolMod executable can go anywhere you want.  No messing about 
      with dopey assigns.

    * Play16 MUST be in the default path.

    * Reqtools.library in LIBS:

    * Playsid.library in LIBS:

    * Medplayer.library in LIBS:

    * Install MUI 3.8 while your at it :)
 
    * CoolMod.key into the S: directory (Registered users)
@endnode

